<doc id="2875378" url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=2875378" title="Hájek">
Hájek

Hájek () (feminine Hájková) is a Czech surname.
The word means "a grove" and is the name or part of the name of many Czech municipalities, settlements and other places. 

